{"tid":778371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯：續拋美元反制裁 或以歐元結算","createTime":"2018-08-13T15:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T12:38:42.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f362b78b97135b6efdea7f1c0542d0cbcc86044e","tid":778371,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯：續拋美元反制裁 或以歐元結算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2136767/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%EF%BC%9A%E7%BA%8C%E6%8B%8B%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%20%E6%88%96%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E7%B5%90%E7%AE%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2136767%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25BA%258C%25E6%258B%258B%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%2520%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%25B5%2590%25E7%25AE%2597&d=baXN5%2FMIYVOlq4sSqcn12XIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=548f301c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2136767/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%EF%BC%9A%E7%BA%8C%E6%8B%8B%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%20%E6%88%96%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E7%B5%90%E7%AE%97</a><br />\n<br />\n土耳其里拉危機牽起環球市場震盪。另一遭到美國制裁國家俄羅斯，貨幣盧布同樣大跌。俄羅斯近期為挺盧布，大舉拋售美債。俄羅斯財長西盧安諾夫（Anton Siluanov）稱，俄方會繼續拋售美元資產，亦不排除以歐元結算，反制美國制裁。<br />\n<br />\n美國制裁加上里拉危機夾擊，俄羅斯盧布今日最多挫2.4%，低見69.3573兌1美元，是為2016年3月以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">西盧安諾夫周日稱，俄方會反制美國制裁，包括減少對美國投資，意味繼續拋售美債。<br />\n<br />\n西盧安諾夫指，美元正變成高風險國際結算工具。他表示，目前原油貿易大多以美元結算，但未來不排除接受以歐元或其他可自由兌換貨幣，甚或俄羅斯盧布支付，但暫時無計劃在境內禁用美元。</span><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯今年曾大舉沽空美國國債。俄方在介乎3月至5月之兩個月間，美債持有量由961億美元，急降至149億美元，減幅高達84%。<br />\n<br />\n美國認定俄羅斯叛諜斯克里帕爾（Sergei Skripal）及女兒尤利婭（Yulia Skripal）在英國中毒，是俄方所為，日前宣布針對出口到俄羅斯的軍民兩用高科技產品，實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n美國連串制裁令俄羅斯反美情緒高漲，有議員提出強行關閉在當地營運的美國企業，但西盧安諾夫表明俄方不會這樣做，他稱這些公司有交稅，對經濟有貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n點解唔用盧布或者人民幣結算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41f4c12971456f612eaf738089945e6272cd77c","tid":778371,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f90340bf28e1856a51d390a703c4d9fd61e9fd","tid":778371,"uid":104699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:00:18.000Z","msg":"用人民幣唔麻，紅當當唔好咩"},{"pid":"3eab29ebe34a75636954e23f07a900e55dd636f5","tid":778371,"uid":37375,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"核彈你就多je<br />\n俄佬經濟總量連南泡都未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b07787941f4d16873163fe2b0b3929fcfc3feb","tid":778371,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:01:29.000Z","msg":"呢輪幾個「強國」嘅財金同央行官員講同做啲嘢都好似痴咗線咁..."},{"pid":"ed53844b4a1809c668a0cf647fb2ce0ee429c04e","tid":778371,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"侵侵又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3e5cda7558df3b27571470d72e0bc7f35b08b0","tid":778371,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"俄佬咁大都冇錢到要賣美債?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8dd6ace0e1757b14862aba8f5054447b2eebf4","tid":778371,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:10:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>或</strong></span></span><br />\n做到先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2566ffd3cb285f3b6e661bdca775e6